better country so others

00:02:02.330 --> 00:02:05.980
can have the same
opportunities that I had.

00:02:05.980 --> 00:02:07.790
During this presentation,
I will give you

00:02:07.790 --> 00:02:11.130
some highlights and general
information about Guatemala.

00:02:11.130 --> 00:02:13.850
Then I will present some facts
about the judicial system,

00:02:13.850 --> 00:02:15.800
and the role of the
International Commission

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:19.150
Against Impunity,
