society as a whole.

00:37:09.580 --> 00:37:12.790
Many years ago,
Edmund Burke said

00:37:12.790 --> 00:37:16.820
that the only thing necessary
for the triumph of evil

00:37:16.820 --> 00:37:19.070
is for good men to do nothing.

00:37:19.070 --> 00:37:23.580
That means that apathy
is the enemy of justice.

00:37:23.580 --> 00:37:25.990
But we do not want Guatemala
or any other country

00:37:25.990 --> 00:37:27.620
to be a failed state.

00:37:27.620 --> 00:37:28.860
